ConstValues.value: "Accept contactless payments with only an iPhone."

"With Tap to Pay on iPhone and the PayEngine app, you can accept in-person, contactless payments, right on your iPhone - from physical debit and credit cards, to Apple Pay and other digital wallets - no extra hardware needed. Its easy, secure and private"
"How to accept contactless cards with Tap to Pay on iPhone."

"1. Enter the purchase amount in your iPad or Web POS app and check out with Tap to Pay on iPhone.
              
2. Present your iPhone to the customer.

3. Your customer holds their card horizontally at the top of your iPhone, over the contactless symbol.

4. When you see the done checkmark, the transaction is complete."
"How to accept Apple Pay and other digital wallets with Tap to Pay on iPhone."

"1. Enter the purchase amount in your iPad or Web POS app and check out with Tap to Pay on iPhone.

2. Present your iPhone to the customer.

3. Your customer holds their device near your iPhone, over the contactless symbol.

4. When you see the done checkmark, the transaction is complete."
